description:
The Second Day Before Christmas: Episode Eight is narrated by King Herod. He explains why he was so upset when the Magi came looking for a new king of the Jews, and why he killed so many babies because of their visit. 

King Herod tells why his family will have such a big impact on the followers of Jesus.  He explains why he is so brutal, and why he reacts so violently when the Magi come to him.

Eyewitness Bible Series is pleased to present the Christmas Series. This series is a collection of 10 new episodes designed to be watched on the three Sundays prior to Christmas week, plus the seven days of Christmas week, ending on Christmas Day.

Scripture: Matthew 2
